"v.欺骗，哄骗 【英】 v. 欺骗，哄骗 (mislead; deceive; trick) 【记】 de+lude(玩弄)→玩弄 别人→欺骗 【同】 同根词：allude(暗示 ); ludictous(可笑的) 【例】 Don't delude yourself with false hopes. v. 欺骗, 哄骗 = mislead = deceive = trick 【记】de, lude玩弄一玩弄别人一欺骗 【参】allude(vi 暗指; 间接提到); ludicrous(adj 可笑的; 愚蠢的) 【类】delusion: thought = hallucination: perception『mirage: imagination』错觉是错误思考 = 幻觉是错误感觉『幻想: 想象』 【记】lud - play 演奏，提起，perception. De + lude 给人假的感觉 【相关】delusion的动词，假的感觉，illusion 幻觉，allude 间接提到 暗指，collude(共谋，勾结)，delude（欺骗 deceive），elude（躲避 escape the perception, understanding），interlude 两段之间的时间，prelude 前奏，postlude 终曲， delude (v.)  c.1400, from Latin deludere ""to play false; to mock, deceive,"" from de- ""down, to one's detriment"" (see de-) + ludere ""to play"" (see ludicrous). Related: Deluded; deluding."
